21-02-02T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">林鄭月娥：在英國時最開心</span>"},{"pid":"e3c383cc07aa507c964b2a5bb6b2c2bf4408d5b3","tid":2392244,"uid":71583,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HkGYRE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkGYRE8.jpg&h=f6a0ddc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723c2e9ad7003402ed07f2d0e36af893dc4f9eed","tid":2392244,"uid":389613,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人用 BNO 係搬石頭砸中共春袋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來用 BNO 離開係 Trump 一早 set 左比中共既計時炸彈！我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本１：支共反制 BNO 引致百國聯軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>支共無錢發難</ins><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２A：支共無錢發難引致世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[軍事小說] 習近平氏の希特拉化！英美德法荷日印澳同盟國形成！普京：依家局勢好似二戰前既30年代！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCmQrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCmQrS</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"0ff92ca7f38fe3b63893f67be5622f772b56fd27","tid":2392244,"uid":2054,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥 在英國時最開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNmx4EVX7dM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTNmx4EVX7dM&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=71b62541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TNmx4EVX7dM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/09/m9H5Yc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F09%2Fm9H5Yc.jpeg&h=886f4fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d2b2d5e7889ac79e695e0ed952af0f2b72a3d30","tid":2392244,"uid":65439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0e0105c7bce6753a45ed1bd86ee76c3c9158005","tid":2392244,"uid":107419,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"經濟問題經濟解決。<br />\n柒婆你開放HKNO護照比英國人過黎香港住law...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"CNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公廁護照"},{"pid":"800d99eea875a4bf77195378fc5d1a5bd483ae95","tid":2392244,"uid":144024,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味，冚家英籍好撚心就收聲算啦<br />\n<br />\n一面講到英國有幾衰有幾背信棄義，但自己屋企又係咁奶。<br />\n連自己個仔都唔撚信妳講嘅嘢，但又迫全港聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實唔出聲無人話佢啞㗎"},{"pid":"19f69326d8150ba8d7842819e79b606d001c63a7","tid":2392244,"uid":351028,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"一個全家攞英國護照話返英國唔講信用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如叫英國捉佢叛國罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5683a13c1d588c4925f164ea31c23fa2ccfbd0b7","tid":2392244,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"吹得我鐘意比錢英國呀 關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45393992b09234a37632c09650ea1bfc2bed89af","tid":2392244,"uid":297152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"柒婆家人全部英籍"},{"pid":"8a7ebf7bd3f17a92d79b9b5d1eb2386c449e51e6","tid":2392244,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"佢老公同兩個仔應該想即時開佢拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81571fb98ffe5a6c2d8ec3d199cb1daf77c72fb","tid":2392244,"uid":9542,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:25:26.000Z","msg":"英國的地產發展商也明顯視港人為主要銷售對象，過去兩星期的主要報章，有多達20個關於英國樓盤的廣告，<br />\n<br />\n好多都係香港公司扮黎厄香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她認識的本港企業家，就有幾位在倫敦擁有整幢商業大厦，這些都是實實在在的經濟利益。<br />\n<br />\n你啲fd 心甘情願買人啲野咁都可以屈返人轉頭，咁你屋企有英澳肉、生果蛋係咪又係人地呃你買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友越黎越痴線，幾時捉返佢入青山"},{"pid":"64feb54bb74d6b19ddafb558b9f4016f18184b85","tid":2392244,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"070e9f87a007f11e32d13738772b9a43e2a22bb8","tid":2392244,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網頁談及有關特區政府不承認BNO作為有效旅行證件和身分證明。她表示，特區政府早前在新聞公告中，暗指英方冒背信棄義之名，實際上有經濟利益的考慮。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，香港一直是英國重要的外來投資來源地，英國是香港向外投資排名榜上的第六名，截至2019年年底投資額達2800億港元；根據2018年數字，而香港則排在英國外資來源地第12位。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，英國的地產發展商也明顯視港人為主要銷售對象，過去兩星期的主要報章，有多達20個關於英國樓盤的廣告，她認識的本港企業家，就有幾位在倫敦擁有整幢商業大厦，這些都是實實在在的經濟利益。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，香港和英國有長期的商貿合作，她在2017年上任後不久便訪問英國，開拓更大的合作空間，指出這才是為自身經濟發展的正道，而非以政治包裝，滿口歪理，甚至違背承諾，為經濟目的護航。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573733-20210202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573733-20210202.htm&d=FM8