經濟目的護航。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573733-20210202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573733-20210202.htm&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d9c42e4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573733-20210202.htm&h=f4d4fba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573733-20210202.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"全家英籍"},{"pid":"2246e3eb1188d6c174e9940d7d99c8b7723adcbd","tid":2392244,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"幾時冚家退出英國籍啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510cbe99acab27661186dcac9a0c08eb833bdd00","tid":2392244,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"都唔知佢講乜鳩"},{"pid":"85a3292673dc4067146e574344823c5b1fcbbbfa","tid":2392244,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f09f2abf466017f0b9cddb92541adc9064ca163","tid":2392244,"uid":261478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T00:05:42.000Z","msg":"英國咁撚衰<br />\n快d叫你老公同d仔放棄英藉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T01:47:51.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n香港記者幾時先識問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ec1cab2325f4bb679e20231a3efcb3ff8b6c4a","tid":2392244,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TNmx4EVX7dM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTNmx4EVX7dM&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d5890818\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TNmx4EVX7dM</a><br />\n柒婆原來最開心喺英國<i